# Rory Terminal

Rory Terminal provides Matrix-style terminal animations and modern terminal customization with Starship integration. Transform your terminal experience with cyberpunk aesthetics!

## Features

- **5 Unique Themes**: Halloween, Christmas, Easter, Hacker, and Matrix
- **Matrix Rain Animations**: Theme-specific colors and symbols
- **Starship Prompt Integration**: Modern, fast, and customizable prompts
- **Windows Terminal Integration**: Automatic profile and color scheme setup
- **PowerShell Module**: Easy theme management with cmdlets
- **GUI Theme Selector**: Visual theme selection and preview
- **Cross-Platform**: Works on Windows, macOS, and Linux

## Quick Start

After installation, use the following PowerShell commands:

```powershell
# Import the module (added automatically to profile)
Import-Module RoryTerminal

# See available themes
Get-RoryTheme

# Change theme
Set-RoryTheme -Name hacker

# Run Matrix animation
Start-RoryMatrix -Theme halloween

# Open GUI selector
Show-RoryThemeSelector
```

## Windows Terminal Integration

The installer automatically configures Windows Terminal with:
- Custom Rory Terminal profile
- All 5 color schemes
- Keyboard shortcuts (Ctrl+Alt+R for new Rory tab)

## What's Included

- PowerShell module with theme management cmdlets
- Matrix animation scripts for all themes
- Starship configurations
- Windows Terminal integration
- Desktop and Start Menu shortcuts
- Theme selector GUI

## Requirements

- PowerShell 5.1 or higher
- Windows Terminal (recommended)
- Starship (optional, for enhanced prompts)
